summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting from Henry W. Schomburg and Wilma J. Schomburg, his wife, and Charles A. Schomburg and Alfreda Schomburg, his wife, a deed and gift of a portion of Lot 12, Block H, A.A. Denny's 4th Addition to the City of Seattle and portions of Lot 12, Block 174, Seattle Tide Lands, in the Pike Place Urban Renewal Project.
